OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fwindy, with further showers through
OL,7,Fthe evening and overnight. Again, some
OL,8,Fof these will be on the heavy side,
OL,9,Fwith the risk of hail. Feeling cold in
OL,10,Fthe brisk winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FAnother day of sunny spells
OL,13,Fand scattered showers is expected.
OL,14,FShowers may be a little less frequent
OL,15,Fthen Saturday. Winds remaining brisk,
OL,16,Fthough gradually easing through the
OL,17,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
